title: UFYB 34: Living with Intention
itunes:title: Living with Intention
description:
So many of us go through life without really making decisions for ourselves or understanding the decisions we made. Then one day, we wake up and find ourselves surprised at how we got to where we are, not sure if we even wanted it for ourselves. So how do you break that cycle of living by someone else’s rulebook and getting the results you don’t want in your life?

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfckyourbrain.com/34
